OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779555957
OL,3,CTech and childhood are intertwined
OL,4,Cmore than ever before, can they co-
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FITV News North of England Reporter
OL,8,FJonathan Brown followed half a dozen
OL,9,Fof the pupils, aged between four and
OL,10,F17, as they swapped their smart
OL,11,Fdevices for so-called "brick phones"
OL,12,Fwithout internet or social media.
OL,14,FThe question for parents about when
OL,15,Fthey should give their child a
OL,16,Fsmartphone is a difficult one; some
OL,17,Fpupils at Ecclesfield School in
OL,18,FSheffield got their first device aged
OL,19,Fseven.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
