PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779555957
OL,3,CTech and childhood are intertwined
OL,4,Cmore than ever before, can they co-
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FAlmost every one of the 1,750
OL,8,Fsecondary pupils there now has one.
OL,10,FBut the fact that around 70 children
OL,11,Ffrom Ecclesfield and its feeder
OL,12,Fschools wanted to try living without
OL,13,Ftheir smartphones for three weeks,
OL,14,Fsuggests some are questioning the
OL,15,Fbenefits that they actually get from
OL,16,Fliving so much of their lives online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
