PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779555957
OL,3,CTech and childhood are intertwined
OL,4,Cmore than ever before, can they co-
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FWe followed half a dozen of the
OL,8,Fpupils, aged between four and 17, as
OL,9,Fthey swapped their smart devices for
OL,10,Fso-called "brick phones" without
OL,11,Finternet or social media.
OL,13,FIt comes as the Government considers
OL,14,FAustralia-style plans to ban under-16s
OL,15,Fin the UK from social media platforms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779555957
OL,3,CTech and childhood are intertwined
OL,4,Cmore than ever before, can they co-
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FOne 14-year-old pupil, Maliah Sibanda,
OL,8,Ftold us she regularly spends 13 hours
OL,9,Fa day on her phone, while teachers
OL,10,Ftold us they had seen that one pupil
OL,11,Fhad spent as long as 20 hours on their
OL,12,Fphone in a single day at a weekend.
OL,14,FThe impact of that, both staff and
OL,15,Fstudents said, was that some young
OL,16,Fpeople were struggling to sleep, get
OL,17,Fto school on time or pay attention in
OL,18,Fclass.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779555957
OL,3,CTech and childhood are intertwined
OL,4,Cmore than ever before, can they co-
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FSome even told teachers they would
OL,8,Foften rush their food at home so they
OL,9,Fcould get back to their screen, such
OL,10,Fwas the draw of what they were seeing.
OL,12,FWe were also told about the darker
OL,13,Fside of their largely unregulated
OL,14,Fsmartphone use, like the exposure to
OL,15,Fexplicit and violent content
OL,16,Fcirculated among social groups, and
OL,17,Fthe impact that had on their mental
OL,18,Fwell-being.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
