PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779555957
OL,3,CTech and childhood are intertwined
OL,4,Cmore than ever before, can they co-
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FBut for the pupils we spoke to, most
OL,8,Fof whom recognised smartphones were
OL,9,Fnot always a productive use of their
OL,10,Ftime, the concern was that losing them
OL,11,Fcould mean losing friends.
OL,13,FStanley Sheldon, who spent six hours a
OL,14,Fday on his phone prior to the project,
OL,15,Fsaid isolation and missing out on the
OL,16,Flatest TikTok trends or memes was a
OL,17,Fmajor anxiety.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
