PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779555957
OL,3,CTech and childhood are intertwined
OL,4,Cmore than ever before, can they co-
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FThere was also a reliance on online
OL,8,Fplatforms for homework - largely gone
OL,9,Fare the days that assignments are
OL,10,Fhanded out on paper - while parents
OL,11,Ftold us they used smartphones to keep
OL,12,Fan eye on their child's location after
OL,13,Fschool.
OL,15,FSmartphone use and the use of social
OL,16,Fmedia clearly have their positives and
OL,17,Fnegatives, but following the project,
OL,18,Fit became apparent that many children
OL,19,Fand their phones are now almost
OL,20,Finseparable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
